        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h1 id="Manchester-City"><a href="#Manchester-City" class="headerlink" title="Manchester City"></a>Manchester City</h1><p><img src="/images/manchester/017DC841C847C693801B2F315AD4F5F8.png" alt="017DC841C847C693801B2F315AD4F5F8"></p><ol><li><p>罗德里 逆足世界波，B席神助攻</p><p><img src="/images/manchester/784fda03ly1hcwfox1wkhj22jl2jlb29.jpg" alt="784fda03ly1hcwfox1wkhj22jl2jlb29"></p></li><li><p>格拉利什逼抢，脚后跟磕给哈兰德，助攻B席，头球轻松破门</p><p>曼城再下一城，比分来到 <strong>2:0</strong></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/784fda03ly1hcwfn7bpeoj20u011iwob.jpg" alt="784fda03ly1hcwfn7bpeoj20u011iwob"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/784fda03ly1hcwfohlp3jj21510nbaxe.jpg" alt="784fda03ly1hcwfohlp3jj21510nbaxe"></p></li><li><p>阿尔瓦雷斯回追，左脚传门前，斯通斯头球做给哈兰德，捅射得分。</p></li></ol><p><img src="/images/manchester/784fda03ly1hcwfmcmxpoj235s23uqv5.jpg" alt="784fda03ly1hcwfmcmxpoj235s23uqv5"></p><hr><p><img src="/images/manchester/990B1236597FDE6221560CA679CEE3B7.png" alt="990B1236597FDE6221560CA679CEE3B7"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/B8D1A81906070D82DE037BA1B178516A.png" alt="B8D1A81906070D82DE037BA1B178516A"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/BBE311CB9659D32FB0EAD31D21FEACE0.png" alt="BBE311CB9659D32FB0EAD31D21FEACE0"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/2D58FA9AE024D5582CDED0960255BA27.png" alt="2D58FA9AE024D5582CDED0960255BA27"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/3A6A9E28A47D7A13B16DF8C5C77E3B90.png" alt="3A6A9E28A47D7A13B16DF8C5C77E3B90"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/EBB73B34A1E23F0137FB6F4179098FBA.png" alt="EBB73B34A1E23F0137FB6F4179098FBA"></p><p><img src="/images/manchester/242029F27098A8FCA10C8E9E38ABB41D.png" alt="242029F27098A8FCA10C8E9E38ABB41D"></p><hr><p>最终，第一场较量双方以 <strong>3:0</strong> 结束</p>]]></content>
      
      
